sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant NM as "NodeManager (Java)"
    participant LCE as "container-executor (Binary)"
    participant Config as container-executor.cfg
    participant Socket as Docker Unix Socket
    participant Daemon as Docker Daemon

    NM->>LCE: Launch Container with Docker arguments
    LCE->>Config: Read configuration constraints (registries, capabilities)
    Note over LCE: Validate user, group, capability restrictions
    LCE->>Socket: Write Docker commands (REST over unix://var/run/docker.sock)
    Socket->>Daemon: Create & Start Container
    Daemon-->>LCE: Container Process ID (PID)
    LCE->>NM: Return Container PID
